              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="testimonial-card">
            <div purpose="quote-mark">“</div>
            <p purpose="testimonial-quote">Our most senior engineers refused to give up Linux. With Fleet, we stopped fighting them. They keep Linux, we get visibility and control. Everyone wins. Our CISO stopped asking about those devices.</p>
            <div purpose="testimonial-attribution">
              <div purpose="testimonial-avatar">P</div>
              <div purpose="testimonial-role">
                <p purpose="role-name">Platform Engineering</p>
                <p purpose="role-team">IT Infrastructure</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div purpose="testimonial-card">
            <div purpose="quote-mark">“</div>
            <p purpose="testimonial-quote">Fleet’s Linux vulnerability coverage is what sold us. We can see CVE exposure across Ubuntu, RHEL, and Debian in the same query. That’s something no other MDM vendor has shipped.</p>
            <div purpose="testimonial-attribution">
              <div purpose="testimonial-avatar">S</div>
              <div purpose="testimonial-role">
                <p purpose="role-name">Security Operations</p>
